    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear you about the serotonin stuff but i'm already feeling pretty bad with the zoloft. if i just take a few days off the sertraline to clear it out of my system before i start the st johns wort, would that be okay? i just want to get on something natural and feel normal again without the doctor drama.",
